# Serve the terminal directly at the root while it's the focus. This is a
# rewrite (status 200), not a redirect -- the browser URL stays "/", the
# content served is app.html. /app still independently works too (nothing
# else changes), so no existing links (Stripe success_url, subscription-gate,
# pricing.js) need touching. index.html/css/landing.css/js/pricing.js are
# untouched and simply unreferenced by this rule -- easy to revert by
# deleting this file whenever the landing page comes back into play.
/  /app.html  200
